stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_receive: receive valid beacon_block or data_column_sidecar from gossip
    q_receive --> q_query_el: call engine_getBlobsV2
    q_query_el --> q_check_all_blobs: check if ALL blobs matching kzg_commitments retrieved
    q_check_all_blobs --> q_no_blobs: not all blobs retrieved
    q_check_all_blobs --> q_convert: all blobs retrieved
    q_no_blobs --> [*]: abort
    q_convert --> q_import: convert blobs to data columns and import
    q_import --> q_check_subscribed: check if subscribed to data_column_sidecar_subnet_id
    q_check_subscribed --> q_publish: subscribed to subnet (custody or sampling)
    q_check_subscribed --> q_update_cache: not subscribed to subnet
    q_publish --> q_update_cache: publish data_column_sidecar on subnet
    q_update_cache --> [*]: update anti-equivocation cache
